plot: Timmy and Chloe go to the retirement home to visit Cat-Man. Cat-Man mistakes Chloe for his old sidekick and takes her on ridiculous hero duties, while Cosmo is stumped on what to give Wanda for their anniversary/Timmy wishes that his Dad could be the mayor of Dimmsdale, but all the attention of being the mayor's son could lead to the exposure of Cosmo and Wanda.—DeJon Diaz
